title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Nissan Navara 2015-on 2.3L ST NP300 4×4 D23 YS23 DOHC Di 16V – Donaldson Pre Filter Fuel Water Separator Dual Bracket Kit OS-17-FS

content.rendered:
Donaldson Fuel Water Separator Kit
Nissan Navara 2.3L ST NP300 (2015 on)
D23 YS23 DOHC Di 16V

**TO FIT MUST HAVE a Vehicle Specific Bracket !!
Included within the OS-PROV-17B Kit >

This kit fits directly onto our Provent Catch Can kit using the same bracket, utilising one bracket for two very important uses and protecting your vehicle ! This Fuel Water Separator kit will not cause flow restriction as it is capable of 114 lph of fuel flow.

Contaminated fuel can lead to vehicle downtime and costly repairs, especially to expensive common rail systems and components. Modern engines are increasingly requiring better fuel fiLation technology to ensure delivery of the cleanest fuel to your vehicle’s fuel system.

Kit OS-17-FS includes:
1x Head Assembly
1x Donaldson Fuel Filter, Water Separator Spin-on
1x Bowl – Twist and Drain
1x rubber hose
2x Brass 90 Degrees Fittings
2x Plastic 90 Degrees Fittings
2x QuickFit Brass Fittings
2x Nuts & Bolts
1x Tube of Thread Sealant
2x Clamps

Filter Element Specifications:
Efficiency: ß11= 100 (99% @ 11 micron)
Water Separation Properties

Download PDF Installation Instructions >
